## MAIN INFO ##
pagistart kay create mo new environment didto idagan

REPO NI NKO

## How to Create Environment :  Run sa Terminal##
python -m venv nameofENV
eg: python -m venv AdBot

Pang activate:
WIN : myenv\Scripts\activate
LINUX/OS: source myenv/bin/activate
eg: AdBot\Scripts\activate

if gagamit ka'g CONDA:
conda create --name myenv
conda create --name myenv python=3.9 -- pang specify

Pang activate:
conda activate myenv


## Needed To DO in the terminal ##
pip install google-generativeai streamlit python-dotenv langdetect nltk


## Version Needed ##
python 3.9+ daw dapat 
python --version
version nko is : Python 3.12


since public atong gHub Repo  :
  - create ".env" file
  - create API_KEY = "your-api-key"

 ## CONSOLE BASED INFO ##
Irun ni before ang main.py IF using console :
Powershell:
$env:API_KEY = "your-api-key"

pero kung cmd ka kay 
set API_KEY = "your-api-key"

ani ka magrun (for the console):
python main.py

 ## ADDITIONAL INFO ##
kita nyo yang .gitignore:
change mo lang into the folder of ur environment. 
In my case, AdBot.

## GUI INFO ##
To run:
strealit run file/path
eg: streamlit run d:/AdmissionBot/admissionBot/main.py
